name: Victorian Mix
description:
I made models of Baroque and Victorian styles based on famous paintings from the 18th and 19th centuries. I hope you enjoy it together.

Do not use it for commercial purposes.

我以18-19世纪的名画为基础，制作了Baroque和Victorian风格的模型。
希望你也一起享受。

请勿用于商业用途。
